title: High-Profile Case Brings New Attention To Oregon's Assisted Suicide Law
teaser: Over the weekend, Brittany Maynard used Oregon's Death with Dignity law to end her own life. Since Oregon's law first passed in 1994, hundreds have used it to prevent suffering at the ends of life.
